2.00	RPG_Life_Sciences	RPG Life Sciences	RPG Life Sciences (RPGLS) is an Indian Pharmaceutical Company. Formerly known as Searle (India) Ltd, RPG Life Sciences is part of RPG Enterprises. It has its corporate office in RPG House in Worli, Mumbai. Its three major activities are manufacturing and marketing of bulk drugs, also known as API, (Active Pharmaceutical Ingredients), pharmaceutical formulation and fermentation &amp; biotechnology. RPGLS is present in the domestic as well as the international market. It exports its products primarily to Europe, Latin America, Australia &amp; South East Asian countries.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5b/MainLogoBig.JPG/300px-MainLogoBig.JPG
